":"推"},{"pid":"536703e21f68d1cef449542d3c096beb93997b6f","tid":1463140,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:06:13.000Z","msg":"阻遊客上機即係將遊客當成人質，真必無必要咁樣做塞機場目的係令國際關注香港而唔係令國際社會厭惡香港"},{"pid":"e86e39e251902b2c05f49a0186609ff075abe4da","tid":1463140,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"536703e21f68d1cef449542d3c096beb93997b6f","tid":1463140,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:06:13.000Z","msg":"阻遊客上機即係將遊客當成人質，真必無必要咁樣做塞機場目的係令國際關注香港而唔係令國際社會厭惡香港"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:08:32.000Z","msg":"厭惡既係香港政府<br />\n關注香港有咩用？<br />\n要關注g20無關注咩？<br />\n成2個月無關注咩？<br />\n要令旅客搵大使館幫手<br />\n大使館唔會比壓力黑衣<br />\n只會比壓力政府<br />\n更有可能出旅遊警告"},{"pid":"8e58cb87a0b183be089de0b7e1853ce36b3c3899","tid":1463140,"uid":251414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:08:49.000Z","msg":"「破解機場民意論」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463130</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e87404bba11854311633da7158fb05f625acfaaf","tid":1463140,"uid":237528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:09:14.000Z","msg":"BBC記者：香港機場「和理飛」絕不應變成「停你飛」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463114\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463114</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cb1c8038494e6172acff3b025c2c4d70a4c151cb","tid":1463140,"uid":267568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59e63e7723dbf4d4797d821d86f7a55f82a912df","tid":1463140,"uid":259284,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:18:25.000Z","msg":"次次一有威脅到政權嘅活動出現，<br />\n就有民意燃衝出黎大叫失民意呀失民意呀，<br />\n都唔知係五毛定真心膠，<br />\n你地真心覺得有抗爭方式係有效而又乜人都阻唔到?<br />\n遊行靜坐都會阻路俾人屌架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港又唔係民主政府，會聽民意，<br />\n你仲想攬住民意過世?  <br />\n文宣到有700萬人同你一齊遊行，政權就會屈服?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文宣到全世界強烈譴責，佢地就會出兵幫你打政府?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己香港要靠自己救，唔係淨係有民意就得，<br />\n任何威脅到政權嘅方法都要試，<br />\n各有各做，核彈都唔割"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:09:15.000Z","msg":"事實上公安會阻遊客<br />\n係咪想一齊？"},{"pid":"2034e642da14c60a51c167324f7939087561c5c8","tid":1463140,"uid":77170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:09:32.000Z","msg":"政府只想借機懲罰國泰 <br />\n國泰係香港既基地邊個最想整死佢<br />\n香港航空，佢阿爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n離境大堂停人唔停貨運 只係自high<br />\n機場最賺錢係貨運<br />\nBlock人 對機場無影響 對旅客大影響<br />\n站在旅客角度，佢地唔會同情，只會令佢地生厭，扣曬印象分<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n站在POPO角度，有藉口清場，情況好似2014雨傘運動，玩唔長<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住你地係和平表達 <br />\n好似 <span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">812咁 示威區+讓出旅客通道</span></span><br />\n宣傳我地HongKongers既理念<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不割蓆 不分化</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 勿忘初心</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef6581ff98b7f59e22cda70a454aba40208e34f2","tid":1463140,"uid":237528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:09:53.000Z","msg":"BBC記者：香港機場「和理飛」絕不應變成「停你飛」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463114\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463114</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nBBC 講 自己諗下"},{"pid":"06224a6e0cc601b9a83fe84bdcb3073893e30a17","tid":1463140,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:14:06.000Z","msg":"樓主講得好<br />\n完全正確"}]}